  <entry>
    <title>Controller 接收多个json对象</title>
    <url>/2021/11/15/JsonParam/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>在写 <code>Spring Boot</code> 加 <code>Vue</code> 项目时,发现由 <code>Spring MVC</code> 提供的@RequestBody 注解在一个方法内,只能有一个。</p>
<p>但是分页外加条件查询需要接受俩个对象参数,经过一番搜索后也是得到了几种不同的解决方法,各有各的优点,视情况和需求选择使用</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="1-url-加-请求体"><a href="#1-url-加-请求体" class="headerlink" title="1.url 加 请求体"></a>1.url 加 请求体</h2><p>将分页需要的信息通过url拼接的方式传给后台,将json对象放在body请求体中</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sndshun/hosting/img/uTools_1637043775953.png" alt="uTools_1637043775953"></p>
<p>请求工具是 <code>axios</code> 会将params属性里的json对象自动拼接到url,需要注意的是 <code>@RequestBody</code> 只能放在参数第一位</p>
<h2 id="2-再次封装实体类"><a href="#2-再次封装实体类" class="headerlink" title="2.再次封装实体类"></a>2.再次封装实体类</h2><p>封装实体类</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Data</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@AllArgsConstructor</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@NoArgsConstructor</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">PageAndPictureDTO</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Page&lt;Picture&gt; page;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> Picture picture;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>前端传入的 <code>json</code> 对象</p>
<figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;page&quot;</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">&quot;current&quot;</span>: <span class="number">1</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">&quot;size&quot;</span>: <span class="number">5</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;picture&quot;</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">&quot;name&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">null</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">null</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><code>Controller</code> 接收</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@RequestMapping(&quot;list&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> R <span class="title">test</span><span class="params">(<span class="meta">@RequestBody</span> PageAndPictureDTO dto)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">     <span class="keyword">return</span> R.ok(<span class="keyword">this</span>.pictureService.getAll(dto.getPage(),dto.getPicture()));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="3-自定义MVC参数处理器"><a href="#3-自定义MVC参数处理器" class="headerlink" title="3.自定义MVC参数处理器"></a>3.自定义MVC参数处理器</h2><p>定义注解</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Documented</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Target(ElementType.PARAMETER)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="meta">@interface</span> JsonParam &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//是否脱敏 默认大小写敏感</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">boolean</span> <span class="title">insensitive</span><span class="params">()</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> <span class="keyword">false</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>编写参数处理器</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">JsonResolver</span> <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title">HandlerMethodArgumentResolver</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">final</span> String JSON_REQUEST_ATTRIBUTE_NAME = <span class="string">&quot;JSON_REQUEST_BODY&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">/**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     * 返回值为true时才调用resolveArgument()</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     *</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     * <span class="doctag">@param</span> methodParameter</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     * <span class="doctag">@return</span> boolean</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     */</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">boolean</span> <span class="title">supportsParameter</span><span class="params">(MethodParameter methodParameter)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 参数是否有@JsonParam注解</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> methodParameter.hasParameterAnnotation(JsonParam.class);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">/**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     * 解析json参数,并反序列化</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     *</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     * <span class="doctag">@param</span> methodParameter       是spring对被注解修饰过参数的包装，从其中能拿到参数的反射相关信息。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     * <span class="doctag">@param</span> modelAndViewContainer</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     * <span class="doctag">@param</span> nativeWebRequest</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     * <span class="doctag">@param</span> webDataBinderFactory</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     * <span class="doctag">@return</span> 根据json反序列化后的对象</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     * <span class="doctag">@throws</span> Exception</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     */</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> Object <span class="title">resolveArgument</span><span class="params">(MethodParameter methodParameter, ModelAndViewContainer modelAndViewContainer, NativeWebRequest nativeWebRequest, WebDataBinderFactory webDataBinderFactory)</span> <span class="keyword">throws</span> Exception </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 获取参数注解</span></span><br><span class="line">        JsonParam jsonParam = methodParameter.getParameterAnnotation(JsonParam.class);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 获取前端传入的数据</span></span><br><span class="line">        String jsonBody = getRequestBody(nativeWebRequest);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 无数据传入直接返回</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (jsonBody.isEmpty()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 创建jackson对象,设置jackson只序列不为空和JavaBean所拥有的属性</span></span><br><span class="line">        ObjectMapper objectMapper = <span class="keyword">new</span> ObjectMapper()</span><br><span class="line">                .setSerializationInclusion(JsonInclude.Include.NON_NULL)</span><br><span class="line">                .disable(DeserializationFeature.FAIL_ON_UNKNOWN_PROPERTIES);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        objectMapper.configure(MapperFeature.ACCEPT_CASE_INSENSITIVE_PROPERTIES, jsonParam.insensitive());</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 获取Controller中参数的类型</span></span><br><span class="line">        Class clazz = methodParameter.getParameterType();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 存放泛型类型</span></span><br><span class="line">        Class Superclass = <span class="keyword">null</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 获取参数类型及泛型类型</span></span><br><span class="line">        Type classParameterizedType = methodParameter.getGenericParameterType();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 判断是否泛型的实例</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (classParameterizedType <span class="keyword">instanceof</span> ParameterizedType) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 强转为泛型</span></span><br><span class="line">            ParameterizedType parameterizedType = (ParameterizedType) classParameterizedType;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 获取第一个泛型Type,强转为Class</span></span><br><span class="line">            Superclass = (Class) parameterizedType.getActualTypeArguments()[<span class="number">0</span>];</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 如果参数类型是list,返回ArrayList,list无法newInstance()</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (clazz == List.class) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            clazz = ArrayList.class;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 实例化</span></span><br><span class="line">        Object target = clazz.newInstance();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 判断是否为集合类型</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (Collection.class.isAssignableFrom(clazz)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 设置jackson反序列化时的类型</span></span><br><span class="line">            JavaType javaType = objectMapper.getTypeFactory().constructParametricType(clazz, Superclass);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// jackson反序列化为对象</span></span><br><span class="line">            target = objectMapper.readValue(jsonBody, javaType);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            target = objectMapper.readValue(jsonBody, clazz);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> target;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">/**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     * 获取请求体JSON字符串</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     *</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     * <span class="doctag">@param</span> webRequest mvc封装后的请求体</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     * <span class="doctag">@return</span> 前端传入的json</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     */</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">private</span> String <span class="title">getRequestBody</span><span class="params">(NativeWebRequest webRequest)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        HttpServletRequest servletRequest = webRequest.getNativeRequest(HttpServletRequest.class);</span><br><span class="line">        String jsonBody = (String) webRequest.getAttribute(JSON_REQUEST_ATTRIBUTE_NAME, NativeWebRequest.SCOPE_REQUEST);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (jsonBody == <span class="keyword">null</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                jsonBody = servletRequest.getReader().lines().collect(Collectors.joining(<span class="string">&quot;\n&quot;</span>));</span><br><span class="line">                webRequest.setAttribute(JSON_REQUEST_ATTRIBUTE_NAME, jsonBody, NativeWebRequest.SCOPE_REQUEST);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span> (IOException e) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            e.printStackTrace();</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> jsonBody;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>将编写的参数处理器注册</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Component</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">WebMvcConfig</span> <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title">WebMvcConfigurer</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">addArgumentResolvers</span><span class="params">(List&lt;HandlerMethodArgumentResolver&gt; resolvers)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        WebMvcConfigurer.<span class="keyword">super</span>.addArgumentResolvers(resolvers);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//配置自定义处理器</span></span><br><span class="line">        resolvers.add(<span class="keyword">new</span> JsonResolver());</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sndshun/hosting/img/uTools_1637050412679.png" alt="uTools_1637050412679" style="zoom:33%;" />

<p><a href="https://docs.apipost.cn/preview/28bf59b888c9069c/71437f5c10135a51">这里可以查看用法</a></p>
<h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>除此外还有别的解决方法,这篇就先分享本人常用的三种.</p>
<p>关于这三种方法缺点也是很明显.</p>
<h3 id="url-加-请求体"><a href="#url-加-请求体" class="headerlink" title="url 加  请求体"></a>url 加  请求体</h3><p>这种方法显然是只能接受俩个对象的,如果要加入第三个对象,是接收不到的.并且url有着长度限制.</p>
<p>但是如果只是传俩个对象,这种方法最为便利,不用对项目做任何更改</p>
<h3 id="封装实体类"><a href="#封装实体类" class="headerlink" title="封装实体类"></a>封装实体类</h3><p>这种方法不怎么灵活,每次参数组合改变都要新建一个封装类.</p>
<p>个人项目经验还不够丰富,不知道配合DTO层用这种方法是不是会好很多</p>
<h3 id="自定义MVC参数处理器"><a href="#自定义MVC参数处理器" class="headerlink" title="自定义MVC参数处理器"></a>自定义MVC参数处理器</h3><p>用这个方法会使小项目结构变得复杂,并且使用了 <code>jackson</code> 进行反序列化,spring boot本身集成了 <code>jackson</code> 这个包,但如果是ssm项目还需导入,或者换成阿里的 <code>fastJson</code> .</p>
<p>项目本来就很复杂,并且有着各种类,用这个方法配置一次,之后就随意使用了.</p>
]]></content>
